    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<h1>約西</h1><ol><li><p>約瑟、馬利亞的歌的另一種音譯，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:3\">馬可福音六章3節</a>。<em>見</em><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"5617\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleBibleDictionary\">約瑟#7</span>。</p></li><li><p>和合本常譯為約瑟。他在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:36\">使徒行傳四章36節</a>中也被稱為巴拿巴。<em>見</em><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"3180\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleBibleDictionary\">巴拿巴</span>。</p></li></ol>",
